Communications Manager
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/04/29 06:52:36
Ref. JB3045310
Job Description
The person holding this role will be responsible for all of the Communications within the Marketing Unit. He/she will be dealing with the UAE media on a day to day basis, and is expected to be the driving force for all Media relations within the organisation with the assistance of an Assistant Manager and Senior Executives.
Skills
Bilingual (English/Arabic)
Good network of contacts in the Media industry.
Strong leader, quick thinker with leadership qualities.
